    <!doctype html>
    <html>
    <head>
        <title>About <%=shopData.shopName%></title>
        <link rel="stylesheet"  type="text/css" href="/main.css" />
    </head>
    <body class="homepage">
        <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="nav-left">
            <a href="/" class="nav-logo"><%= shopData.shopName %></a>
        </div>

        <ul class="nav-center">        
            <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="/meals/list">All meals</a></li>
            <li><a href="/workouts/list">All Workouts</a></li>
            <li><a href="/auth/register">Register</a></li>
        </ul>

        <div class="nav-right">
            <a href="/auth/login" class="login-btn">Login</a>
            <a href="/logout" class="login-btn">Logout</a>
        </div>
        </nav>
        <div class="index-container" style="text-align: left;">
        <h1>About <%= shopData.shopName %></h1>
        <p>
            <%= shopData.shopName %> is a simple health and fitness application designed to help users 
            track their workouts, meals, and overall progress. The goal of this app is to make it easy to 
            build healthy habits by keeping all your fitness information in one place.
        </p>

        <p>
            This app was created as part of the Dynamic Web Applications module and demonstrates key full-stack 
            concepts such as routing, database integration, searching, form handling, authentication, 
            and dynamic page rendering using EJS.
        </p>

        <h2>Key Features</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Log workouts with exercise name, duration, and calories burned</li>
            <li>Record meals and track daily calorie intake</li>
            <li>Search your workout or meal history using database queries</li>
            <li>View summaries and recent activity on your dashboard</li>
            <li>Simple login system with session authentication</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            <%= shopData.shopName %> brings these technologies together to create a clean, functional, 
            and user-friendly fitness tracking experience.
        </p>

        <p class="already-member" style="margin-top:25px;">
            Already registered? <a href="/auth/login">Click here</a>
        </p>
        </div>
    </body>
    </html>